{"tid":909206,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★Apple已die！蘋果最大組裝廠鴻海市值跌破萬億台幣大關","createTime":"2018-11-20T07:58:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-20T08:01:29.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ef19c84fc7909a91abb53e72b1938cc5fbe28ada","tid":909206,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T07:58:52.000Z","msg":"IT之家11月20日消息 蘋果最大組裝廠鴻海市值跌至9，857億元台幣，這是自2013年11月以來其首次失守萬億大關<br />\n<br />\n據悉，鴻海年迄今累計跌40%，邁向2008年金融危機以來最差年度表現。此前據台灣《經濟日報》報導稱，受新iPhone銷量以及明年全球經濟情勢等不確定因素影響，鴻海集團近期計劃降低人力成本和固定費用。<br />\n<br />\n鴻海財報顯示，今年第三季度，因生產旺季配合出貨放大與生產效率提升，結合成本管控，單季淨利潤回升至56億元人民幣，同比增長18.3%；不過，今年前三季度淨利潤約149.5億元人民幣，同比減少0.9%。<br />\n<br />\n蘋果的最新財報顯示增長持平，並表示將停止披露季度智能手機銷售數據。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ithome.com/0/395/901.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ithome.com%2F0%2F395%2F901.htm&d=Q2fpNZjU8e7BPMXOjrwcQaEKYqckrLkk14koP0tj2xA%3D&h=f4459fbe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ithome.com/0/395/901.htm</a>"},{"pid":"0b6e38d4d5461ffb9860602134e97eb5fe0817ee","tid":909206,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T07:59:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec1725fa35df1807d27136a5a1816c8ac34726d7","tid":909206,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T08:00:07.000Z","msg":"Nokia is waiting Apple<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42b6ec63fff5eb82b313b39549def78440468620","tid":909206,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T08:01:29.000Z","msg":"鴻海係自己減資20%wo<img src=\"/a